Date: Mon, 23 Dec 2019 17:20:25 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 1855/4530] drm/i915: Add Wa_1408615072 and Wa_1407596294 to
 icl,ehl

Workaround database indicates we should disable clock gating of both the
vsunit and hsunit.

